'''David Nakayama''' (born [[August 15]], [[1978]]) pencilled the comic "[[The Apprentice (comic story)|The Apprentice]]."

He also did the covers for the first three issues of the miniseries [[Star Wars: Han Solo - Imperial Cadet]].

